<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٨٥٧ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5542">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ حَاتِمٍ </a>قَالَ: أَنْبَأَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1269">‌حِبَّانُ </a>قَالَ: أَنْبَأَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3875">‌عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1610">‌حَمَّادٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">‌</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِبْرَاهِيمَ ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2313">‌أَبِي سَعِيدٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِذَا اسْتَأْجَرْتَ أَجِيرًا فَأَعْلِمْهُ أَجْرَهُ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>